HEADWORD: Devisor
<hw>De*vis"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>One
who devises, or gives real estate by will; a testator; -- correlative to
<xex>devisee</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Devitable</ent>⟦br⟧
